{"tid":1394890,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當元朗示威前, 連登幾千個正評講唔好搞黑社會彰顯公義, 今日所謂既公義, 就係朱凱迪受死亡恐嚇","createTime":"2019-08-01T14:36:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T15:30:57.000Z","uid":44171,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"29d669567acf24814e5076c413421d2f75f17836","tid":1394890,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:36:49.000Z","msg":"你搞完黑社會, 黑鄉, 就成個新界義士都會俾人打死.<br />\n<br />\n你滅左村又點? 你自己都變成黑社會<br />\n<br />\n俾人打, 更加要用和平俾全世界睇示威者俾正義一方.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我屌你老母個臭化西啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n你唔撚推埋你老母老婆出去元朗俾黑社會輪大米以示公義？叫埋自己仔女俾黑警打多2掍向全世界以示和平？<br />\n<br />\n成日問之後點？家下就之後啦, 最和平善良果個反而受死亡威脅, 呢d就係你地既光環, 你地既公義, 你地想要既國際睇法, 你地要既中間派<br />\n<br />\n你地想要既, 我一樣都唔想要, 我只係想屌你老母啦, 俾你老母我屌下, 用你顯示你既公義啦, 仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d6942beeac42d955da656e1c84ba142aa5d8c92","tid":1394890,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:39:09.000Z","msg":"點解朱凱迪成日都話有人要暗殺佢？"},{"pid":"b486aa43a19287540e199aeefc21ddeea20ae8e8","tid":1394890,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d6942beeac42d955da656e1c84ba142aa5d8c92","tid":1394890,"uid":235580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:39:09.000Z","msg":"點解朱凱迪成日都話有人要暗殺佢？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:39:52.000Z","msg":"點解政府成日講市民係暴徒？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c34634002a2b5ab70a482c6e34fdce81acac7bb","tid":1394890,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T14:43:38.000Z","msg":"一個都不能小"},{"pid":"63d075b1823851c9420db6d3dcb48dd8d0391005","tid":1394890,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2